WEBVTT

00:00:39.355 --> 00:00:41.983
Mommy got sick.

00:00:42.058 --> 00:00:44.993
It happened just like that.

00:00:45.061 --> 00:00:48.394
There was nothing anybody could do.

00:00:48.465 --> 00:00:50.456
It isn't fair.

00:00:50.533 --> 00:00:52.524
There's no reason.

00:00:52.602 --> 00:00:57.767
But if we start asking why,
we'll go crazy.

